      "text": [
        " «لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1622 - Ali ibn Ja'far asked his brother Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) about a man who gives his Zakat for dirhams in the form of dinars, and for dinars in the form of dirhams, based on their value.\nImam (as) replied: \"There is no issue with that.\""
        ]
      }
